query:
SELECT 
    COUNT(*) as total_contracts,
    SUM(CASE WHEN originType='DIRECT' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as direct_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN originType='ASSUMED' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as assumed_count
FROM contracts;

SELECT propertyId, buyerName, originType, contractPrice, downPayment 
FROM contracts 
ORDER BY propertyId;
